#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.delete.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.delete"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.delete.delete:1 of
msgid ""
"Return a new array with sub-arrays along an axis deleted. For a one "
"dimensional array, this returns those entries not returned by `arr[obj]`."
msgstr ""
"返回一个沿指定轴删除子数组的新数组。对于一维数组，这将返回那些不被 `arr["
"obj]` 返回的元素。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.delete.delete of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.delete.delete:5 of
msgid "Input array."
msgstr "输入数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.delete.delete:7 of
msgid "Indicate indices of sub-arrays to remove along the specified axis."
msgstr "指示要沿指定轴删除的子数组的索引。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.delete.delete:9 of
msgid ""
"The axis along which to delete the subarray defined by `obj`. If `axis` "
"is None, `obj` is applied to the flattened array."
msgstr ""
"沿该轴删除由 `obj` 定义的子数组。如果 `axis` 为 None，则将 `obj` 应用于"
"展平后的数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.delete.delete of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.delete.delete:13 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- A copy of `arr` with the elements specified by `obj` removed. "
"Note that `delete` does not occur in-place. If `axis` is None, `out` is a"
" flattened array."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 一个移除了由 `obj` 指定元素的 `arr` 副本。注意 `delete` 不是就"
"地操作。如果 `axis` 为 None，则 `out` 是一个展平的数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.delete.delete of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

